name: Angry Birds Breakfast 1
description: "Angry Birds Breakfast 1" is a breakfast-themed mobile game featuring the iconic Angry Birds characters flinging breakfast foods to defeat green pigs and rescue stolen eggs.

name: Angry Birds Classic
description: "Angry Birds Classic" is the groundbreaking and much-loved mobile game that revolutionized the gaming industry. Developed by Rovio Entertainment, it was first released in December 2009 and quickly became a global sensation. In this addictively fun game, players are tasked with launching a variety of cute and colorful birds from a slingshot to dismantle intricate structures housing pesky green pigs.

name: Angry Birds Rio
description: "Angry Birds Rio" is an exciting installment in the popular Angry Birds franchise, developed by Rovio Entertainment in partnership with 20th Century Fox. Released in March 2011, the game was inspired by the animated film "Rio." In this edition, the Angry Birds are not battling against the usual green pigs but instead find themselves in the vibrant city of Rio de Janeiro, Brazil.

name: Angry Birds Seasons
description: "Angry Birds Seasons" is a captivating spin-off of the popular Angry Birds franchise, developed by Rovio Entertainment. Released in October 2010, the game introduces a seasonal theme, with each level pack corresponding to various holidays and events throughout the year.

name: Angry Birds Space
description: "Angry Birds Space" is a captivating and innovative addition to the beloved Angry Birds franchise, developed by Rovio Entertainment. Released in March 2012, the game takes the classic bird-flinging gameplay to new heights by introducing players to a whole new dimension of physics-based puzzles.

name: Angry Birds Star Wars
description: "Angry Birds Star Wars" is an epic crossover between the world-famous Angry Birds franchise and the iconic "Star Wars" universe. Developed by Rovio Entertainment in collaboration with Lucasfilm, the game was launched in November 2012 and quickly became a massive hit.

name: Angry Birds Star Wars II
description: "Angry Birds Star Wars II" is a thrilling sequel to the successful crossover between the Angry Birds franchise and the legendary "Star Wars" universe. Developed by Rovio Entertainment in partnership with Lucasfilm, the game was released in September 2013.

name: Bad Piggies
description: "Bad Piggies" is a spin-off game from the Angry Birds franchise, created by Rovio Entertainment. Released in September 2012, the game takes a unique perspective by allowing players to take on the role of the mischievous green pigs, who are typically the antagonists in the Angry Birds series.

name: Fnaf: Sister Location
description: In Five Nights at Freddy's: Sister Location, players explore a new animatronic facility, taking on the role of a technician named Mike. The game deviates from the traditional security guard setting and introduces a narrative-driven experience. Players navigate through different sections of the facility, facing unique animatronics and completing tasks. The game includes a mix of suspenseful gameplay and a deeper narrative, shedding light on the dark lore of the FNaF universe.

name: Five Nights At Freddy's 1
description: "Five Nights at Freddy's 1" is a horror game where players work as a night security guard at Freddy Fazbear's Pizza, fending off animatronic characters that come to life. The goal is to survive five nights by monitoring cameras and closing security doors to avoid jump scares from the animatronics.

name: Five Nights At Freddy's 2
description: "Five Nights at Freddy's 2" is the sequel where players work as a night security guard again, facing new animatronics in a different location. There are no security doors, and players must manage a music box to avoid attacks from the Puppet. The game introduces a Freddy Fazbear mask for defense, adding to the suspenseful gameplay.

name: Five Nights At Freddy's 3
description: "In Five Nights at Freddy's 3, players take on the role of a security guard once more, but this time in a horror attraction. The main threat is Springtrap, a decommissioned animatronic, haunted by a vengeful spirit. The game introduces a unique mechanic involving audio devices to lure Springtrap away. The atmosphere is tense as players navigate through a haunted location while trying to survive the night."

name: Five Nights At Freddy's 4
description: "In Five Nights at Freddy's 4, players assume the role of a child trying to survive a series of nights at home haunted by nightmare versions of animatronic characters. Unlike previous games, there is no security office; instead, players must listen for subtle audio cues to anticipate and defend against animatronic attacks. The game features a more intense and personal atmosphere, with a focus on sound and fear of the unknown, making it a unique and challenging installment in the series."

name: Five Nights At Freddy's 4: Halloween Edition
description: "In Five Nights at Freddy's 4, players assume the role of a child trying to survive a series of nights at home haunted by nightmare versions of animatronic characters. Unlike previous games, there is no security office; instead, players must listen for subtle audio cues to anticipate and defend against animatronic attacks. The game features a more intense and personal atmosphere, with a focus on sound and fear of the unknown, making it a unique and challenging installment in the series."

name: Legacy of Flan: Flan Rising
description: "Legacy of Flan: Flan Rising" is an interesting RPG with a unique fighting and leveling system. You play a group of four flans (little marshmallow-like creatures), which all have different strengths and weaknesses. While fighting enemies you can collect drops that change one flan into a new one with new abilities. This way your group will get stronger and be able to fight more powerful foes. But it's not always easy to find the right combination of flans to win a fight. Made by Scott Cawthon in 2003.

name: The Desolate Room
description: "The Desolate Room" is a retro-style indie game developed by Scott Cawthon, the creator of the popular "Five Nights at Freddy's" series. It was released in 2007 and serves as one of Scott's earlier works in game development.

name: Sklepik Nemo
description: "Sklepik Nemo" to symulator, w którym zarządzasz własnym sklepem. Gracze muszą dbać o zaopatrzenie, obsługę klientów i rozwój swojego biznesu, aby osiągnąć sukces. Gra oferuje różnorodne wyzwania związane z prowadzeniem sklepu, co sprawia, że jest interesująca i wciągająca.

name: Było Sobie Życie - Oddychanie
description: Gra edukacyjna “Było Sobie Życie - Oddychanie” od Hippocampus to unikatowy tytuł, który pozwala graczom na poznanie mechanizmów oddychania i funkcjonowania układu oddechowego w ludzkim ciele.

name: CubiQ
description: Stara gra dodawana do zestawu CD razem z grą "Sklepik Nemo"
